@NODE acc "Access level configuration"
From version 2.02 you may define some options to use with the accesslevels.
You may name the different accesslevels and you may choose if the
multitasking should be enabled or not. During the login segments the
multitasking is always disabled but when you reach the menus a user with
enabled multitasking will be able to switch between the AmiMUS and WB using
LAmiga+A and break the program with Ctrl+C.
@ENDNODE

@NODE future "The future"
If you have any suggestions, comments or bugreports please write and tell
me. But here are some things I plane to include in a future version of
AmiMUS anyway...

	A lot more functions in the login, scriptfiles and in the menus
	Some sort of localization
@ENDNODE
	
